    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "WESTBON",
      "QUEEN OF THE WESTERN AIRLINES FLEET IS\nTHE DC-6B — symbol of air service in the West.\nCarrying 60 passengers in super-pressurized,\nfour-engine comfort, Western's DC-6Bs fly\nthe Routes of the CALIFORNIAN,\n\"champagne\nand orchids\" flights serving major cities of the West.\nWESTERN AIRLINES • AMERICA'S SENIOR AIRLINE\nPOST CARD\nUSE\nAIR\nMAIL"
